snippets.snippet: "RIGOLETTO SHORT HILLS" is located at the hill side under Komazawa street." The first floor features a comfortable, breezy terrace, and the main dining room where traditional Arabic patterns shimmer radiantly. The second floor provides a relaxing atmosphere with the warm Moroccan-style interior and fireplace.
